description: The FTSE World Government Bond Index - Developed Markets in EUR terms aims to reflect the performance of the following markets: Fixed rate debt issued by governments of developed countries Exposure across the whole yield curve (minimum time to maturity of 1 year) Investment grade bonds only FX hedged exposure into EUR Additional information on the Index and the general methodology behind the FTSE Russel indices can be found on FTSE Russel Index website ( https://www.yieldbook.com/ ).
name: Xtrackers II Global Government Bond UCITS ETF 1D EUR Hedged
